Heuristic:
1. Flexibility and efficiency of use
2. User control and freedom
3. Aesthetic and minimalist design

Problem:
1. The data log page should provide a search button to search through time/value data the user wants and look through older data. 
2. All the pages should have exit buttons so that the user can go back to the last stage efficiently. 
3. The map of the farm is unnecessary on the main page in the advanced mode.  

Solution:
1. Search input bar and button added. 
2. Exit button added. 
3. Map removed. 

Serverity:
1. 2
2. 1
3. 2
